title: Rock Band Country Track Pack 2 [SRCE69] (wbfs)
description:
Rock Band: Country Track Pack 2

      Get out those boots and shine up that belt buckle. It is time for another trek up the country charts with the Rock Band Country Track Pack Volume 2! Give a tip of your cowboy hat to your favorite artists as you perform 21 more country favorites in classic Rock Band modes like Quickplay, Tug of War, and Solo or Band Tour. The set list includes George Strait's "Twang," Lady Antebellum's "Perfect Day," Jason Aldean's "Crazy Town," Luke Bryan's "Rain is a Good Thing," "Giddy on Up" by Laura Bell Bundy, "Summer Nights" from Rascall Flatts, and many more. 

Song List Includes:

Stage one (5 songs)

1. Merle Haggard-Mama Tried
2. Johnny Cash-Ring Of Fire
3. Chely Wright-Single White Female
4. Darius Rucker-Alright
5. Dwight Voakam-Intentional Heartache

Stage 2 (5 songs)

6. Lady Antebellum-Perfect Day
7. Billy Currington-That's How Country Boys Roll
8. Darryl Worley-Awful Beautiful Life
9. Jason Aldean-Crazy Town
10. Luke Bryan-Rain Is a Good Thing

Stage 3 (5 songs)

11. Sugarland-Settlin'
12. George Strait-Twang
13. Dierks Bently-Sideways
14. Gary Allen-Man Of Me
15. Reba McEntire-The Night The Lights Went Out In Georgia

Stage 4 (6 songs)

16. Justin Moore-Backwoods
17. Trace Adkins-Ride
18. Laura Bell Bundy-Giddy On Up
19. Keith Urban-Kiss a Girl
20. Rascal Flatts-Summer Nights
21. Shania Twain-Party for Two (with Billy Currington)
